member.name: F:SemVer.PreReleaseStage.ALPHA
member.summary: This typically means that work on major features is still ongoing.

member.name: F:SemVer.PreReleaseStage.BETA
member.summary: This typically means that major features are complete, though not necessarily bug-free or tested, and may or may not mean that minor features are done or tested.

member.name: F:SemVer.PreReleaseStage.RC
member.summary: This typically means that all planned features or changes are either done or cut, as well as tested and mostly ready. Code should be mainly stable.
